{

  "private": true,
  "version": "0.0.0",
  "type": "module",
  "scripts": {
    "dev": "vite",
    "build": "npm-run-all clean build:client build:ssr prerender publish:docs generate:seo",
    "build:docs": "cross-env VITE_BASE_PATH=/mark-hazleton-s-notes/ VITE_SITE_URL=https://markhazleton.github.io/mark-hazleton-s-notes SITE_URL=https://markhazleton.github.io/mark-hazleton-s-notes npm run build",
    "build:client": "vite build",
    "build:ssr": "vite build --ssr src/entry-server.tsx --outDir docs/server",
    "build:dev": "cross-env NODE_ENV=development vite build --mode development",
    "build:prod": "cross-env NODE_ENV=production vite build",
    "lint": "eslint .",
    "lint:fix": "eslint . --fix",
    "preview": "vite preview",
    "clean": "rimraf docs",
    "prebuild": "npm run clean",
    "generate:seo": "node src/scripts/generate-seo-assets.mjs",
    "prerender": "node src/scripts/prerender.mjs",
    "publish:docs": "node src/scripts/publish-docs.mjs",
    "type-check": "tsc --noEmit",
